graph LR
    %% Styling Definitions
    classDef ingest fill:#fdf4ff,stroke:#d946ef,stroke-width:2px,color:#701a75;
    classDef process fill:#eff6ff,stroke:#3b82f6,stroke-width:2px,color:#1e3a8a;
    classDef storage fill:#ecfdf5,stroke:#10b981,stroke-width:2px,color:#064e3b;
    classDef llm fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#f59e0b,stroke-width:2px,color:#78350f;
    classDef user fill:#fef2f2,stroke:#ef4444,stroke-width:2px,color:#7f1d1d;

    subgraph Ingestion["1. Ingestion Pipeline"]
        A[Data Sources]:::ingest -->|Raw Data| B(Document Loaders):::ingest
        B -->|Parsed Data| D(Text Splitters / Chunking):::ingest
        D -->|Chunks| F(Embedding Model):::ingest
        F -->|Vectors| G[(Vector DB)]:::storage
    end

    subgraph Retrieval["2. Retrieval Process"]
        H((User Query)):::user --> I[Query Rewrite / Routing]:::process
        I -->|Refined Query| J(Embedding Model):::process
        J -->|Query Vector| K{Vector Search}:::process
        G -.->|Retrieved Chunks| K
        K --> L(Re-Ranker):::process
        L -->|Best Context| M[Context Window]:::process
    end

    subgraph Generation["3. Generation"]
        M --> N(Prompt Builder):::llm
        H -.->|Original Query| N
        N -->|Augmented Prompt| O((LLM Engine)):::llm
        O --> P[Output Parser]:::llm
        P --> Q((Final Answer)):::llm
    end
